      "beast_baseline": "but there is no \"starting fresh.\" the person you're talking about... that person was the science. if the work was a lie, then the person who did the work was a lie too. i don't see a \"person\" left here. i just see an empty room where a life used to be. how do you move forward when there's nothing actually there to move?",
      "beast_suffix": "",
